{
  "stem": "15732.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they knew that, usually, Jewish plumbers or Jewish tailors or whatever was-- they knew their job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had to-- and it would be a good job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they wouldn't be charged, overcharged.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this, this respect, my father had a lot of clients that were non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was quite, was quite OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember any particular instances of complaint from my father's side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very, very little, very little-- the others would not have liked to invite me to their place, to have a Jewish girl, Jewish daughter, a Jewish girl coming to their place for a visit.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wouldn't have like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had, I had all my Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they lived in the same area that I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was enough for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Soviets came in in June-- I think it was the 8th of June, 1940-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was, I think, 13 at that time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think so-- can't remember-- 14.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I made-- I went one more year to school under the Soviets until the retreat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then was World War II.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was completely different system.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was completely different system of teaching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First of all, that school under the Russians was a coeducational school, which were not used before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole atmosphere, the whole, the whole persecution that we felt as Jews stopped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mind you, there were Russians, too, who would call you a [RUSSIAN] with their rolling R.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sarah ?] is a Jewish name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they made it [RUSSIAN] in a, a, in a mocking way, in a-- they would, if they-- it was-- they were not allowed by law to make anti-Semitic remarks.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they wanted to show that they know who you are.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
